

Setup:

  Cadmium Nodes:


  Cadmium2 Nodes:

    Node1: ec2-204-236-188-218.us-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com
    Mode2: ec2-50-18-140-208.us-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com

    Dev: http://dev.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/
    QA: http://qa.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/
    Staging: http://staging.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/
    Prod: http://prod.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/

    cadmium deploy git@github.com:meltmedia/test-content-repo.git http://dev.cadmium2.meltdemo.com
    cadmium deploy git@github.com:meltmedia/test-content-repo.git http://qa.cadmium2.meltdemo.com
    cadmium deploy git@github.com:meltmedia/test-content-repo.git http://staging.cadmium2.meltdemo.com
    cadmium deploy git@github.com:meltmedia/test-content-repo.git http://prod.cadmium2.meltdemo.com


Preparing the environment:

    cadmium commit out0 http://dev.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "Setup"
    cadmium clone http://dev.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ http://qa.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "Setup"
    cadmium clone http://qa.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ http://staging.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "Setup"
    cadmium clone http://staging.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ http://prod.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "Setup"

Running the Demo:

  Content 1:
    cadmium commit out1 http://dev.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "Step 1"

  Content 2:
    cadmium commit out2 http://dev.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "Step 2"

  Example push to prod:
    cadmium clone http://dev.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ http://qa.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "To QA"
    cadmium clone http://qa.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ http://staging.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "To Stage"
    cadmium clone http://staging.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ http://prod.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "To Prod"

  Content 3:

    cadmium commit out3 http://dev.cadmium2.meltdemo.com/ -m "Step 3"
